OL,3,CHeadteacher launches knife crime
OL,4,Clessons after son's fatal stabbing
OL,6,FA junior school headteacher has
OL,7,Fintroduced lessons warning children
OL,8,Fabout the dangers of knife crime after
OL,9,Fher own son was stabbed to death.
OL,11,FAlison Castledine's 22-year-old son
OL,12,FDanny suffered 44 stab wounds in a
OL,13,Frandom attack while travelling in
OL,14,FAmsterdam two years ago.
OL,16,FHis killer, a Belgian national, was
OL,17,Fjailed for 14 years in January.
