OL,3,CHeadteacher launches knife crime
OL,4,Clessons after son's fatal stabbing
OL,6,FHis killer, referred to in court only
OL,7,Fas Nongo B, was a drug addict. The
OL,8,Fcourt heard there was no obvious
OL,9,Fmotive for the attack.
OL,11,FDanny's sister Chloe designed the
OL,12,Flessons and said she would like to see
OL,13,Fthem taught in all schools.
OL,15,F"What brings it home for me is that
OL,16,Fthese children should have their whole
OL,17,Flives ahead of them just like I should
OL,18,Fhave had my whole life ahead of meI'm
OL,19,Fa victim of knife crime just as much
OL,20,Fas Danny was a victim of knife crime,"
OL,21,Fshe said.
