OL,3,CHeadteacher launches knife crime
OL,4,Clessons after son's fatal stabbing
OL,6,FChief executive Patrick Green said:
OL,7,F"We know from the statistics we see
OL,8,Fthat knife carriers are getting
OL,9,Fyounger, thankfully those numbers are
OL,10,Fstill small but its important we act
OL,11,Fnow to eradicate those young people
OL,12,Fbout the dangers carrying knives.
OL,13,FTrusted adults - including teachers -
OL,14,Fare vital in that process."
